      "statement": "theorem procedural_associator_cocycle_fcb095da7572 : (\u2200 {M : Type _} [Monoid M] [HasDistribNeg M] {a b : M}, Associated a (-b) \u2194 Associated a b) \u2192\n  ((\u2200 {R : Type _} [NonUnitalNonAssocRing R] (a b c d : R),\n      a * associator b c d - associator (a * b) c d + associator a (b * c) d - associator a b (c * d) +\n          associator a b c * d =\n        0) \u2227\n    (\u2200 (\u03b1 : Type _) [Ring \u03b1], IsDomain \u03b1 \u2194 NoZeroDivisors \u03b1 \u2227 Nontrivial \u03b1)) := by\n  sorry",
